The user can drug back the nutrients.

fields.description:
Data Export: Will be done manually on request from the admin
 - Add an 'Export' page with a list of export requests
and an export button on each request that will download the exported data described in the following section.
- Export will include:
a CSV of the user's personal details and login details
a CSV of the user's sessions data
a CSV of the user's session average
fields.customfield_10402:
As a user, I would be able to receive an email with all the details collected on me
1. The user would be able to tap the "export my details" button 
2. After tapping the button, a pop-up will appear explaining that we have received his request and that the user will receive in a short while an email with all his details
3. The user would be able to close the pop up by tapping the okay button
3.1 If the user's request has failed (no internet connection etc.,) the user will see a pop up telling him something went wrong and to try again

The admin
1. The admin will have a section called "Export information"
2. This section will include a table with user's requests for their information
3. The table will include the next details: 
3.1 The requesting user's name 
3.2 The requesting user's email address 
3.3 "Download" button for each requesting user
3.4 "delete" button for every request 

Export By Admin
1. By clicking an email address the admin would open a new email message with the email he clicked on
2. By clicking the download button, the admin will download to his computer a CSV including the next details -  
2.1 user's personal details and login details
a CSV of the user's sessions data
2.2 user's sessions data
2.3 user's session average
3. By clicking the "delete" button the admin will be able to delete a user's request

fields.customfield_10402:
filter foods by groups will be a popup
The header "סינון קבוצות" will be on the top of the popup
The sub header "בחירת קבוצות מזון אשר אימון רצויות בתפריט" will be under the header
Two tabs will switch the content of the table:
מאכלים נפוצים
מאכלים נוספים
the content will come from the DB
In the table, the headers will be the categories.
The content will be the groups.
Clicking on a group, will mark the group in red and will make this group disappear from the "add food" suction.
Clicking on a group that all ready in red, will cancel the red mark and bring the group to be enable again on the "add food" suction.
Clicking on a header (Category) will act the same as clicking on a group, but will effect all of his groups.
If a category are mark in red (and all of his groups) and the user are clicking  on a red group
Switching between the tabs wont delete the changes.
Clicking on the "X" or the "Cancel" button will open a popup "are you sure you want to close.."
Clicking on the "Save" button will save the changes and go back to the "Menu settings".
